{"tid":473414,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次同鬼佬上床有問題","createTime":"2017-11-19T08:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T04:01:35.000Z","uid":51701,"like":23,"dislike":325,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"1140e4f8c85a103f6f2be48ed18f8e8e5dcf67e8","tid":473414,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:19:15.000Z","msg":"昨晚與上司上床，佢射係我大比，㸃知佢射完揸住佢弟弟係我陰唇磨幾下又插入去，一段時間佢射係我陰毛，隨後又塞入去，應該連一部分精液插埋入去，如事者第三次射我Pat pat<br />\n<br />\n我第一次同鬼佬做，唔知佢地射完仲硬，我22碎之前拍過兩次拖，男人不是一射就軟嗎？我係安全期但佢咁帶體外精液入去容易有BB嗎？"},{"pid":"e328e00e7110f21646aca1f14b0328a7938b9253","tid":473414,"uid":20622,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be7220e0ec18783b132b8f5833deabd9b0ff4b2","tid":473414,"uid":57447,"like":184,"dislike":1,"score":183,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"22碎 有問題嗰個係你"},{"pid":"27d6caf5f2335c0b6471b15bccf4379d96a6524e","tid":473414,"uid":23058,"like":174,"dislike":1,"score":173,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"你自己係男人都唔知?"},{"pid":"7abebc0c68cd5d1d7a2982959998b8c5bf5b67cb","tid":473414,"uid":26899,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:23:36.000Z","msg":"咁你射喺佢邊個位先"},{"pid":"2b4f9c8f2527da9b21c65235f70babe162dd1dc0","tid":473414,"uid":9104,"like":121,"dislike":2,"score":119,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:23:52.000Z","msg":"放心 男人是不會懷孕"},{"pid":"3480ed4d7b2921e2f78173457aacfbd3f3d02ad8","tid":473414,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己係男人都唔知?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\